C                 STATISTICAL ENGINEERING DIVISION
C                 INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY LABORATORY
C                 NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF STANDARDS AND TECHNOLOGY
C                 GAITHERSBURG, MD 20899-8980
