C
C-----CHARACTER STATEMENTS FOR NON-COMMON VARIABLES-------------------
C
      CHARACTER*4 IHARG
CCCCC AUGUST 1995.  ADD FOLLOWING LINE
      CHARACTER*4 IHARG2
